      <title>外国投资者将结束亚洲新兴市场股票购买势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/foreigner-investors-set-to-end-emerging-asia-stock-buying-streak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球资金正在从亚洲新兴市场撤出，连续五个月的股票购买热潮因美国降息预期的减弱而结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/foreigner-investors-set-to-end-emerging-asia-stock-buying-streak</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 06:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本维权基金将在年度股东大会上推动大同首席执行官下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/japan-activist-fund-to-push-for-daidoh-ceo-s-ouster-at-agm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由丸木刚 (Tsuyoshi Maruki) 领导的激进基金战略资本公司 (Strategic Capital Inc.) 将推动大同株式会社 (Daidoh Ltd.) 总裁下台，此前这家服装制造商多年经营亏损。]]></description>
